              into Osakana's executable and not statically linked.

  FFmpeg
    License : GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1 or later (LGPL-2.1+)
              with optional GPL-2.0+ components (x264, x265, etc.) when
              BtbN's "gpl" build variant is used.
    URL     : https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html
    Notes   : Downloaded at runtime as a standalone executable
              (BtbN gpl build on Windows / Linux, evermeet.cx on macOS)
              and invoked as a separate process. NOT bundled into
              Osakana's executable. Because the binary is fetched
              independently and only invoked across a process boundary,
              this is "mere aggregation" and does not affect Osakana's
              MIT license.

  aria2 (optional)
    License : GNU General Public License v2 (GPL-2.0)
    URL     : https://github.com/aria2/aria2/blob/master/COPYING
